{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/ketemu-sama-topeng-kosong-di-sfx-show-the-monster-annual-2nd-collection-exhibition/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Ketemu sama Topeng Kosong di SFX: Show The Monster Annual 2nd Collection Exhibition","content":"\n<p><em>Weekend </em>gini bingung mau ke mana? Kehabisan ide buat cari inspirasi? atau hanya ingin sekedar melepaskan penat? Mungkin ke Plaza Indonesia solusinya. Ada pameran kece yang bisa kamu kunjungi!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yap, hari Jumat kemarin, tepatnya tanggal 15 November 2019, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"CIAYO Comics (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>CIAYO Comics</strong></a> berkesempatan untuk hadir dalam pembukaan pameran<strong> Show The Monster Annual 2nd Collection Exhibition</strong>. Brand lokal Indonesia yang bergerak di bidang desain karakter ini membuka pameran annual dalam meliris&nbsp;koleksi lini fesyen keduanya yang bertajuk <strong>SFX.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"56565\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ketemu-sama-topeng-kosong-di-sfx-show-the-monster-annual-2nd-collection-exhibition/attachment/imageedit_15_6436382798/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_15_6436382798.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Speaker\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Konferensi Pers rencana pameran SFX: Show The Monster Annual 2 Collection Exibition di GoWork, Plaza Indoneisa, Jakarta (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_15_6436382798-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_15_6436382798.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_15_6436382798.jpg\" alt=\"Show Me The Monster_Speaker\" class=\"wp-image-56565\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_15_6436382798.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_15_6436382798-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Konferensi Pers pameran SFX: Show The Monster Annual 2 Collection Exibition di GoWork, Plaza Indoneisa, Jakarta (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures) </figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Buat kamu yang belum tau, <strong>Show The Monster</strong> berawal dari sebuah tagar <strong>#showthemonster</strong> di Instagram sebagai campaign ilustrasi dari sang <em>owner,</em> <strong>Evan Aditya, </strong>seorang desainer karakter. Setelah sukses dengan campaignnya, akhirnya Show The Monster berdiri sebagai brand desain karakter pada tahun 2018 dan melahirkan karakter-karakter monster baru dengan maskot utama berupa kelinci berwajah &#8220;X&#8221; yang bernama <strong>Topeng Kosong.</strong> Di tahun yang sama, mereka menyelenggarakan debut perdananya dengan merilis lini fesyen pada bulan Mei 2018. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kini, di tahun keduanya, Show The Monster kembali hadir dengan monster-monster baru dalam satu rangkaian pameran yang bertajuk SFX. SFX adalah singkatan untuk <em>special effects</em>. Meskipun terkadang dianggap hanya sebagai tambahan pada suatu konteks, tanpa <em>special effects </em>kita tidak akan mendapatkan dampak yang hebat. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"56561\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ketemu-sama-topeng-kosong-di-sfx-show-the-monster-annual-2nd-collection-exhibition/attachment/imageedit_9_4346646679/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_9_4346646679.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Pengunjung\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Pictures / Fadly Alisjahbana&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_9_4346646679-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_9_4346646679.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_9_4346646679.jpg\" alt=\"Show The Monster_Pengunjung\" class=\"wp-image-56561\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_9_4346646679.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_9_4346646679-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Pictures / Fadly Alisjahbana</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Show The Monster berharap dapat memberikan generasi muda sarana untuk mengekspresikan diri mereka yang unik dengan karakter monster mereka yang berani.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dalam penyelenggaraan annual event SFX Exhibition, Show The Monster juga berkolaborasi dengan <strong>GoWork</strong> selaku&nbsp;<em>Venue &amp; Community Partner</em> yang turut serta mendukung perkembangan industri kreatif di Indonesia. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;Inovasi terbaru yang kami luncurkan adalah membuat&nbsp;<em>creative space&nbsp;</em>di<strong> Plaza Indonesia.</strong> Hal ini merupakan salah satu upaya kami sebagai&nbsp;<em>coworking platform&nbsp;</em>untuk dapat menciptakan ruang acara kreatif dan serba guna untuk memberdayakan member kami&#8221; ujar <strong>Vanessa Hendriadi, CEO &amp; Co-Founder GoWork.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"56564\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ketemu-sama-topeng-kosong-di-sfx-show-the-monster-annual-2nd-collection-exhibition/attachment/imageedit_13_6868592767/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_13_6868592767.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Karya-karya\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Pictures / Fadly Alisjahbana&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_13_6868592767-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_13_6868592767.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_13_6868592767.jpg\" alt=\"Show The Monster_Gambar\" class=\"wp-image-56564\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_13_6868592767.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_13_6868592767-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Pictures / Fadly Alisjahbana</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Tidak tampil sendirian, pameran ini turut serta merangkul rekan-rekan perupa Indonesia di bidang ilustrasi untuk turut serta berkolaborasi dalam kegiatan ini diantaranya adalah <strong>Diela Maharani, Martcellia Liunic, Aditya Pratama, Isa Indra Permana, WD Willy, Criwill dan Robby Garsia. </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tak hanya perupa muda, pameran ini juga menggandeng <strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"CIAYO Comics  (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id\" target=\"_blank\">CIAYO Comics </a></strong>sebagai rekan platform komik Indonesia. Sebagai platform baca komik online terlengkap bagi milenial Indonesia, <strong>CIAYO Comics </strong>bangga dapat mendukung acara ini. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"56560\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ketemu-sama-topeng-kosong-di-sfx-show-the-monster-annual-2nd-collection-exhibition/attachment/imageedit_7_9144015241/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_7_9144015241.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,342\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Pictures / Fadly Alisjahbana&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_7_9144015241-300x169.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_7_9144015241.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_7_9144015241.jpg\" alt=\"Show The Monster_CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-56560\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_7_9144015241.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_7_9144015241-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Pictures / Fadly Alisjahbana</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;Mimpi besar CIAYO Comics adalah membawa IP-IP lokal ke skala yang lebih besar, dalam hal ini skala global. Untuk mencapai titik tersebut, kita harus terlebih dahulu mengenalkan IP lokal ke masyarakat Indonesia yang lebih luas. Dan untuk mewujudkan mimpi itu kami sadar kami gak bisa bergerak sendiri, kolaborasi antar pelaku juga peminat juga diperlukan. Contohnya kolaborasi dengan Show The Monster melalui SFX Exhibition&#8221; ujar <strong>Tonny Hanggoro, Head of Marketing CIAYO Comics. </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dalam pameran ini, <strong>CIAYO Comics</strong> dan para ilustrator juga akan memamerkan karya berupa ‘monster-monster’ buatan sendiri. <strong>CIAYO Comics</strong> juga menggunakan karakter-karakter ini untuk dijadikan komik dan dipajang di GoWork Creative Space.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"56563\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ketemu-sama-topeng-kosong-di-sfx-show-the-monster-annual-2nd-collection-exhibition/attachment/imageedit_11_6330319180/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_11_6330319180.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"548,975\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Scan Barcode\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Pictures / Fadly Alisjahbana&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_11_6330319180-169x300.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_11_6330319180.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_11_6330319180.jpg\" alt=\"Show The Monster_Scan\" class=\"wp-image-56563\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_11_6330319180.jpg 548w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_11_6330319180-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 548px) 100vw, 548px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Pictures / Fadly Alisjahbana</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu juga bisa loh ketemu sama karakter-karakter monster pameran ini di <strong>CIAYO Comics. </strong>Tinggal cek aja judul komik:<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" Topeng Kosong and Friends.  (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/topeng-kosong-and-friends\" target=\"_blank\"> Topeng Kosong and Friends. </a>Atau langsung aja datang ke pameran dan <em>scan barcode</em> di sana buat baca keseruannya!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"56566\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ketemu-sama-topeng-kosong-di-sfx-show-the-monster-annual-2nd-collection-exhibition/attachment/imageedit_19_6052083529/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_19_6052083529.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"imageedit_19_6052083529\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_19_6052083529-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_19_6052083529.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_19_6052083529.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-56566\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_19_6052083529.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/imageedit_19_6052083529-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: GoWork</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Pameran ini masih akan berlangsung selama satu bulan hingga 14 Desember 2019 sebagai seri kegiatan tahunan dari Show The Monster. Yuk, buruan ketemu sama <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Topeng Kosong and Friends (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/topeng-kosong-and-friends\" target=\"_blank\">Topeng Kosong and Friends</a> di GoWork Coworking Space, Plaza Indonesia, Level 5. Siapa tau jadi terhibur. </p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"79f2bf96-55ee-5047-be36-50cbd1e72332"}}}